<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Imaduddin Learning Hub</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#334155);
color:white;
}
.container{
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
padding:40px 20px;
}
h1{
font-size:48px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}
p{
color:#cbd5e1;
}
.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:30px;
}
.card{
background:#1e293b;
padding:25px;
border-radius:18px;
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
transition:0.3s;
}
.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
}
.card h2{
margin-bottom:10px;
font-size:24px;
}
.login input{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin-top:10px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
}
button{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin-top:12px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
background:white;
color:#111827;
}
footer{
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
color:#94a3b8;
margin-top:40px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<h1>Imaduddin Learning Hub</h1>
<p>Grow your English Grammar & Speaking skills with professional learning.</p>

<div class="grid">
<div class="card">
<h2>📘 Basic English</h2>
<p>Grammar, daily speaking, beginner practice.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>📗 Intermediate</h2>
<p>Tenses, writing, confidence speaking.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>📙 Advanced</h2>
<p>Fluency, vocabulary, professional English.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>🎯 IELTS Zone</h2>
<p>Reading, Writing, Listening & Speaking.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="grid">
<div class="card login">
<h2>🔐 Premium Student Portal</h2>
<input type="text" placeholder="Email Address">
<input type="password" placeholder="Password">
<button>Login</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>📜 Certificates</h2>
<p>Earn certificates after course completion.</p>
<br>
<h2>🤖 AI Speaking Checker</h2>
<p>Practice speaking and improve fluency.</p>
</div>
</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Imaduddin Learning Hub | All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
